 * Throws: Nothing.
 *
 * Examples:
 * -----
 * addExt("foo.txt", "raw") => "foo.raw"
 * addExt("foo.", "raw") => "foo.raw"
 * addExt("bar", "raw") => "bar.raw"
 * -----
